folder: East River Drive & 73rd Street (East), Manhattan, NY
text:
East River Drive, at East 73rd Street, showing the garbage loading dock at the waters edge, and a commercial structure separated by this newly completed roadway.

September 28, 1940
No's. 1-2

P. L. Sperr
